{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1113881, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "极佳。windows用于onenote和偶尔用到奇奇怪怪的软件，其他时候ubuntu可以满足所有的需求。\n另外，surface的话win10对触摸屏和笔的支持好很多。", "timestamp": 1613728124, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "wsl就行了", "timestamp": 1613728222, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113886, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz明天装Ubuntu，现在有两个疑问：\n（1）安装系统的时候会格式化系统盘吗\n（2）两个系统下的文件是共享的吗", "timestamp": 1613728275, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么不先试一下虚拟机或者wsl呢？\n毕竟在wsl加持下，windows是当前最好的linux发行版", "timestamp": 1613728343, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113892, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "默认ubuntu可以访问windows文件，但是windows不能访问linux文件", "timestamp": 1613728377, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 虚拟机试过了hhh", "timestamp": 1613728405, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113896, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不会格式化  可自己选择一个磁盘或者分区装ubuntu", "timestamp": 1613728432, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113903, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: dz的电脑只有C盘和D盘，也就是说安装在任何一个分区都可以吗？", "timestamp": 1613728537, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1113910, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: \n（1）在不同分区上装就不会格式化，推荐做法是缩小win10系统分区，装linux时会自动格式化一个新的分区。\n（2）可以做到共享，简单来说和分区格式有关。ubuntu能打开任何分区格式的盘，windows只能打开ntfs/fat格式的分区，无法打ubuntu系统使用的ext4格式分区。", "timestamp": 1613728691, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1114053, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 为何不用 wsl？", "timestamp": 1613731481, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1115618, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 218524, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为何不用 wsl？wsl过香。\n", "timestamp": 1613753465, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 218524, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "有用win10+Ubuntu双系统的dy说下体验吗？\n谢谢orz", "timestamp": 1613727996, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1613753463, "url": "", "vote": {}}}